<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM10.9.7">
<l>āḻiyan tiṇṭē raracarvan tiṟaiñca valaikaṭa lulakamu ṉāṇṭa</l>
<l>pāḻiyan tōḷō rāyiram vīḻap paṭaimaḻup paṟṟiya valiyō</l>
<l>māḻaimeṉ ṉōkki maṇiniṟaṅ koṇṭu vantumuṉ ṉēniṉṟu pōkāy</l>
<l>kōḻiveṇ muṭṭaik keṉceyva tentāy kuṟuntaṭi neṭuṅkaṭal vaṇṇā.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Why the strength when [you] grasped a battle axe so that, when the king</l>
<l rend="indent">with a sturdy-wheeled, beautiful chariot came and bowed down,</l>
<l>One-thousand strong arms fell that had once ruled the earth,</l>
<l rend="indent">its seas roiling?</l>
<l>Having come taking the beautiful complexion of the one of lovely soft glances,</l>
<l rend="indent">remaining before [her eyes], you do not leave [her thoughts].</l>
<l>My lord, [you] the hue of the vast sea, why the use of a short cudgel</l>
<l rend="indent">to crack a white hen’s egg?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
